artefact.licence_overview:
If you market, pack or re-pack, seal or reseal or label or re-label seed, prepare seed mixtures, clean, treat or process seed for marketing you must be licensed by the [Food and Environment Research Agency (Fera).](http://www.fera.defra.gov.uk/ "Food and Environment Research Agency (Fera)"){:rel="external"}

Licences will be issued electronically and will have conditions attached.

Applications can be made by post or online.
